snippet.title: PlayStation - Barbie - Race & Ride (1999) - [Intro]
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Barbie rides onto the PlayStation for the first time ever in an all-new horseback riding game. Gallop through breathtaking snow-capped mountains, a beach at sunset, a beautiful redwood forest and more.
